Breaking change to the `fake-aws-s3` helm chart. We now use minio helm chart from https://charts.min.io. The options are documented [here](https://github.com/minio/minio/tree/master/helm/minio) (#1944)

Before running the upgrade, the operators must use `kubectl edit deployment fake-aws-s3` and explicitly set `spec.template.spec.containers[0].serviceAccount` and `spec.template.spec.containers[0].serviceAccountName` to null.